{"tid":954006,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"邁向手作大師之路--果凍蠟篇","createTime":"2018-12-24T10:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T13:17:12.000Z","uid":64601,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb421b1b20c827d6268b622998174395eb636b3","tid":954006,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"今日就係我 馬丁露乜鳩嘅手作大師之路第一站，真男人就係要風趣得嚟又帶點細心。要帶出細心呢一點，除咗養下小動物之外<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONeHGLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONeHGLi.jpg&h=52e6de2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，冇咁多心機嘅就可以整下手作仔氹下小妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （養寵物係一生嘅承諾，唔好因為一時衝動）<br />\n<br />\n首先，材料好簡單<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2uP59g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2uP59g.jpg&h=b5db5119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有：<br />\n加熱果凍蠟<br />\n燈芯<br />\n沙<br />\n貝殼仔<br />\napm扭蛋公仔<br />\n其他小裝飾<br />\n玻璃樽<br />\n<br />\n一開始就要加熱果凍蠟，成舊dom落去個煲度，用最細最細火慢慢加熱到熔，大火會起泡同埋唔好攪佢。<br />\n<br />\n其間你可以裝飾下你個樽先<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqRZJWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqRZJWM.jpg&h=0ed4d246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M2YZu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M2YZu8.jpg&h=39a1fc3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果凍蠟熔到變水狀就可以收火，攤一陣等佢平靜，用牙籤整走啲泡。之後就慢慢沿樽邊倒落去。有細泡仔係正常嘅，當佢變凍就會少啲㗎啦，又或者你可以用火鎗燒下啲泡位等佢少啲。<br />\n<br />\n完成圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twQjJX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwQjJX8.jpg&h=6265164a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日亦都係我手作大師收山之日，我都係唔好搞咁多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe3ba3e116829b2195242fc9e58f87c9270248c","tid":954006,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b46cc5a54d996b93908747ec028b2f651ef7a070","tid":954006,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:27:51.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b07029ba7f833bb47413e536831c13591852e2e","tid":954006,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1732c5142d7add5401334c04e303e97787bf3d46","tid":954006,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"42e2d2ca79b639da5f3a0d4b921c361b8b76b590","tid":954006,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"完成圖乜柒都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328ec051488502e19e04a225b409772d8b1ba00f","tid":954006,"uid":89538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42e2d2ca79b639da5f3a0d4b921c361b8b76b590","tid":954006,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"完成圖乜柒都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"好多泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69042f508e48f0e00dcd49c26f94bcabf51134fb","tid":954006,"uid":47112,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"嘩 你隻伊貝潛緊水呀"},{"pid":"f9a70b8ea804c200c91faea63c6ac28a5c621724","tid":954006,"uid":19213,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"完成圖似浸尻死隻伊貝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7929cff8c8836ce75db49a62a1f9b89c052ce07","tid":954006,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:29:21.000Z","ms